fields.title: Harris 1993 Wausau Health Care Experiences Survey, study no. 932003

dsDescription.dsDescriptionValue: This survey focuses on fears, concerns, and experiences of health care consumers and providers in Wausau, Wisconsin. Variables include costs, insurance, health status, access to health care, managed care, reform options, impact of health concerns on respondent's life and employment choices.

fields.notesText: Subject: Study Level Error Note, Notes: National random digit dialing; Universe: American adults aged 18 years of age and older.
